    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C/ 200\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Cut your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> in half (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon)</p><p>Top, tail and chop your <strong>courgette[s]</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Cut your <strong>red onion[s]</strong> into quarters, keeping the skin on and root attached</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/balsamic-meat-free-sausages-and-roasted-veg-couscous/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Peel and finley chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chopped veg </strong>and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> to a bowl with a large drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong>,<strong> </strong>season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Add the <strong>seasoned</strong> <strong>veg </strong>to a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!)</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/balsamic-meat-free-sausages-and-roasted-veg-couscous/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> meat-free sausages</strong> to the opposite side of the tray[s]</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 25-30 min until the sausages are golden and cooked through and the veg is starting to brown</p><p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/balsamic-meat-free-sausages-and-roasted-veg-couscous/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 200ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>in a small bowl</p><p>Add your<strong> couscous</strong> to the bowl, then cover and set aside for later</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/balsamic-meat-free-sausages-and-roasted-veg-couscous/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>balsamic</strong> <strong>vinegar</strong> and 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> to a pot over a medium-high heat</p><p>Bring to the boil, then reduce the heat to very low and cook for approx. 2-3 min or until it turns into a runny glaze that coats the back of a spoon</p><p>Tip: Watch the pan like a hawk to make sure the glaze doesn't burn!</p><p>Once done, remove the pot from the heat and set aside until serving \u2013 this is your <strong>balsamic glaze</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/balsamic-meat-free-sausages-and-roasted-veg-couscous/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Fluff the<strong> cooked couscous</strong> with a fork</p><p>Carefully remove the skin from the <strong>roasted onions</strong> by cutting the root end off and peeling off the skin, then separate the onion into petals</p><p>Chop the <strong>roasted pepper</strong> into small pieces</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/balsamic-meat-free-sausages-and-roasted-veg-couscous/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Chop your<strong> basil</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Mix the <strong>roasted</strong> <strong>veg</strong> and <strong>chopped basil</strong> through the couscous \u2013 this is your <strong>roasted veg couscous</strong></p><p>Drizzle with <strong>olive oil</strong> and taste for seasoning, adding more <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> if needed</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/balsamic-meat-free-sausages-and-roasted-veg-couscous/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> cooked meat-free sausages</strong> over the <strong>roasted veg couscous</strong></p><p>Spoon the <strong>balsamic glaze</strong> all over the meat-free sausages</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
